Nakamichi cd-changer			(SCSI)			SONY
Matsushita-Kotobuki (Soundblaster CD)	(ATAPI)			ATAPI

@{UNDERLINED "Soll @{BOLD "NICHT"} funktionieren mit:"}
Aiwa ACD300				(SCSI)
NEC 3X Multispin			(SCSI)
Panasonic CR-506 drive			(SCSI)
Sanyo drives				(SCSI)
Sanyo drives				(ATAPI)
Overdrive/Zappo				(ATAPI)
Mitsumi	FX series			(ATAPI)
Wearnes					(ATAPI)
